item.title: CVE-2023-30591|2024-08-02T14:28:51.967Z -- nodebb%2C%20inc. -- nodebb
item.description: Denial-of-service in NodeBB <= v2.8.10 allows unauthenticated attackers to trigger a crash, when invoking `eventName.startsWith()` or `eventName.toString()`, while processing Socket.IO messages via crafted Socket.IO messages containing array or object type for the event name respectively.
